{"tid":2391991,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"mla出咗新歌啦！！！！","createTime":"2021-02-02T13:57:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T11:42:55.000Z","uid":244352,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"bc92050409177b8df7113d3fb8fd1095867cac9e","tid":2391991,"uid":244352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T13:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n那陣時不知道<br />\n<br />\n曲詞編  林阿p<br />\n唱  nicole au<br />\n和  karena au<br />\n<br />\n如像九十年代初<br />\n照片裡海灘的印象<br />\n那種下午沒有重量<br />\n帶點迷惘奔向夕陽<br />\n<br />\n那年獨自去南洋<br />\n一杯白咖啡的早上<br />\n四周是可冒險方向<br />\n尤加利樹葉的香<br />\n<br />\n那陣時不知道<br />\n置身的日子都發亮<br />\n眼光裡藏著的囂張<br />\n往後已不再同樣<br />\n<br />\n圖書館木製的窗<br />\n訓導假裝嚴肅的模樣<br />\n還未有傾訴對象<br />\n仍未覺得悲涼<br />\n<br />\n那陣時不知道<br />\n每天在風光的戰場<br />\n騎著馬去到邊疆<br />\n所到之地全是賜賞<br />\n<br />\nwoo 寂靜 但不漫長<br />\nwoo 寂靜 但不漫長<br />\nwoo 寂靜 但不漫長<br />\nwoo 寂靜 但不漫長<br />\nwoo<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=5xi49OreS3k&amp;fbclid=IwAR19gDXfKNJf1z7YatvFUZOBsvEUtMRygJM5wGRyK4BEDCvkPYd3MAmpkfg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5xi49OreS3k%26fbclid%3DIwAR19gDXfKNJf1z7YatvFUZOBsvEUtMRygJM5wGRyK4BEDCvkPYd3MAmpkfg&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BOzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=9de47e8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=5xi49OreS3k&amp;fbclid=IwAR19gDXfKNJf1z7YatvFUZOBsvEUtMRygJM5wGRyK4BEDCvkPYd3MAmpkfg</a>"},{"pid":"8f932717890587236e20f7ffb6c0d5891bd439cb","tid":2391991,"uid":240150,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:14:24.000Z","msg":"眼光裡藏著的囂張<br />\n往後已不再同樣<br />\n<br />\n希望我仲識囂張<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8914ec3f3ffdc30a71b3c54348fc584dfc5a31f2","tid":2391991,"uid":390606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi